peration, you must have permission to perform the <code>s3:PutJobTagging</code> action.</p> <p>Related actions include:</p> <ul> <li> <p> <a>CreateJob</a> </p> </li> <li> <p> <a>GetJobTagging</a> </p> </li> <li> <p> <a>DeleteJobTagging</a> </p> </li> </ul>",
