            "description": "<p>Specifies the bucket being deleted.</p> <p>For Amazon S3 on Outposts specify the ARN of the bucket accessed in the format <code>arn:aws:s3-outposts:&lt;Region&gt;:&lt;account-id&gt;:outpost/&lt;outpost-id&gt;/bucket/&lt;my-bucket-name&gt;</code>. For example, to access the bucket <code>reports</code> through outpost <code>my-outpost</code> owned by account <code>123456789012</code> in Region <code>us-west-2</code>, use the URL encoding of <code>arn:aws:s3-outposts:us-west-2:123456789012:outpost/my-outpost/bucket/reports</code>. The value must be URL encoded. </p>",
            "schema": { "type": "string", "minLength": 3, "maxLength": 255 }
          }
